subsection.def:
aerial ropeway (架空纜車索道)
                means an aerial ropeway as defined in section 2 of the Aerial Ropeways
                (Safety) Ordinance (Cap. 211);

commercial GFA (商用總樓面面積),
                in relation to a terminal, means the gross floor area for or ancillary to commercial
                use, as specified in the Project Agreement;

discharge date (解除責任日期)
                means the date referred to in the guarantee agreement, if any, as being the
                discharge date of the guarantee;

guarantor (保證人) means a person
                who for the time being has undertaken the obligations of a guarantor under the
                guarantee agreement, if any;

occupy (佔用), in relation to any
                land, includes use, be in possession of, enjoy, erect or maintain a structure on or
                over, or place or maintain anything on the land;
